name: Unter Null
description: '''Unter Null''', was founded as a solo [[aggrotech]] music project by '''Erica Dunham''' in 1998 at the age of 17, while living in [[Seattle]], United States. {{As of|2012}}, she is based in [[Portland, Oregon]]. Dunham is trained in [[Piano|classical piano]], [[cello]] and [[guitar]]. Live performances consist of Dunham on lead vocals, Brendin Ross (formerly of [[Bile (band)|Bile]]) on keyboards and Krz Souls of [[Dawn of Ashes]] on e-percussion.
